{"tid":2401771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"擅取租戶「淋病月娥」甜批 誠品拒交代","createTime":"2021-02-10T03:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T06:13:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":438,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"48f25a822fa9033c209fa7a43b330aaec2a5db81","tid":2401771,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:53:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/C6DC4KLMQNDFFESHA3WYOVWZBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FC6DC4KLMQNDFFESHA3WYOVWZBU%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQlSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=3e6055cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FC6DC4KLMQNDFFESHA3WYOVWZBU%2F&h=7018f56a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/C6DC4KLMQNDFFESHA3WYOVWZBU/</a><br />\n<br />\n擅取租戶「淋病月娥」甜批 誠品拒交代<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2ay74B_qvFtAzyLZbSAhJXCNNG8=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IS3QVDIDQBDLXFHR3YEXECFQ6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2ay74B_qvFtAzyLZbSAhJXCNNG8%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIS3QVDIDQBDLXFHR3YEXECFQ6Y.jpg&h=d7e2aaa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■日前誠品太古店有職員一度取走黃店BJY藝術烘焙師印有「淋病月娥」等字句的甜批（小圖）。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】在誠品生活太古城分店開業的「黃店」BJY藝術烘焙師日前關店後，三件分別寫上「淋病月娥」、「仆街死」及印有警察開槍圖案的甜批，被人擅自取走半個鐘再放回原位。他引述誠品承認事件，但沒交代取走目的，僅稱會作懲處。店主形容事件十分荒謬，「究竟係因為我哋嘅意見、香港人嘅意見，定係只要唔符合誠品嘅利益，就唔可以存在喺佢舖頭呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n店主斥荒謬<br />\n<br />\nBJY藝術烘焙師在社交平台公開事件，店主Jay接受本報查詢時表示，本月7日下午約6時關門後，賣剩三件朱古力果仁書法甜批，分別寫上「淋病月娥」、「仆街死」及印有警察開槍圖案，存放於售賣甜批的玻璃雪櫃，沒有上鎖。惟翌日朝早收到鄰店店主通知，有誠品職員取走該三件甜批，約半小時後放回原位。<br />\n<br />\nJay隨即趕返店舖了解事件，有誠。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「究竟係因為我哋嘅意見、香港人嘅意見，定係只要唔符合誠品嘅利益，就唔可以存在喺佢舖頭呢？」Jay表示，去年11月獲邀進駐誠品生活太古店，月租約2.4萬元。其店售賣的甜批及糕點都印有社運圖案或「香港人加油」等字句，一直相安無事。<br />\n<br />\nJay續指，店內涉事三件甜批被擅自取走，誠品從沒主動通知店方，「以為擺番落去就扮冇事」，幸得鄰店知會才揭發事件。三件甜批被取走半小時再放回原位，過程中可能受環境污染，甚至不知會否被落毒，亦質疑誠品是否有權擅取租戶私人財產，但至今誠品未具體交代。<br />\n<br />\nJay強調，無論政治立場如何都有權發聲，「如果唔係，你（誠品）當初就唔好向我招租」。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"efc2eef23ccff1300ef4ae8dadf0e545271f92a7","tid":2401771,"uid":125017,"like":110,"dislike":0,"score":110,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:54:37.000Z","msg":"落毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9122f8156215724c70d15ef19260653632edcc6","tid":2401771,"uid":103156,"like":6,"dislike":18,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:57:15.000Z","msg":"篤灰！「作出具煽動意圖的作為」罪"},{"pid":"78dccf1562158fcb9f2c981636f8748ea450c2dc","tid":2401771,"uid":167289,"like":281,"dislike":0,"score":281,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:00:07.000Z","msg":"咁大間公司實有幾個藍員工"},{"pid":"035199091b98dc82928a68a55f9e10acb0b59be1","tid":2401771,"uid":199771,"like":8,"dislike":80,"score":-72,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"應該終止BJY租約<br />\n及要店主對損害誠品形象作出賠償"},{"pid":"8f75eaacecc1ae6a6228407183c85c465fca17a5","tid":2401771,"uid":83251,"like":201,"dislike":0,"score":201,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:16:28.000Z","msg":"奶共店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n向蔡英文告發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a556087eaef4ec06075731752cd15b95f5e2f7","tid":2401771,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:16:44.000Z","msg":"拒咩交代姐<br />\n一句&ldquo;我係藍嘅，支持政府！報驚丫笨！&rdquo;"},{"pid":"76b752380e46d8d14af5b331b3ed31f906138292","tid":2401771,"uid":91771,"like":215,"dislike":0,"score":215,"quote":{"pid":